# Dual Axis Solar Tracker Documentation

## 1. Introduction
The Dual Axis Solar Tracker is an Arduino-based system designed to automatically track sunlight using LDR sensors and servo motors. The project improves solar panel efficiency by maintaining optimal alignment with the sun.

---

## 2. Objectives
- To increase solar energy collection efficiency
- To implement automatic sunlight tracking
- To design a lightweight 3D printed mechanism
- To learn embedded system control using Arduino

---

