## 4. System Architecture
The system consists of:
- Light sensing unit
- Arduino control unit
- Servo motor actuation system
- Solar panel mounting structure

---

## 5. Working Principle
The LDR sensors continuously measure sunlight intensity from different directions. The Arduino compares these values and rotates the servo motors toward the direction of maximum light intensity.

Two servo motors provide:
- Horizontal movement
- Vertical movement

This enables dual-axis tracking.

